name: 2013 Neon Circus Event Tee
description:
Limited Edition! Get the 1st official event T-shirt of the 2013 Neon Circus Music Festival. This Unisex T-shirt features an all-over print created by dye sublimation with Neon Circus's signature Deejay Clown donning the front and the official DJ lineup on the back.

Dye sublimation is a printing technique that allows all-over-printing of full color images with superior softness. Artwork is first printed onto large sheets of high release paper substrate, and the images are then transferred to the garments using heat and pressure. The heat converts the solid dye particles into a gas, and the pressure forces them to bond to the polyester content of the garments. The dye is absorbed by the garment during the sublimation process, which differs from the screen print process, where the ink sits on top of the garment. Slight wrinkles and random spots of missing ink are common in this one-of-a-kind print process.

Please Note: This T-shirt is NOT available for shipping.
T-shirts are expected to be delivered in person on Saturday, September 28th during the Neon Circus Music Festival in Sarasota, FL.
Customers will be notified of any changes in delivery schedule.
